      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm absolutely heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
