    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a peerless 2011 Porsche Cayman S, representing the pinnacle of the 987.2 generation. This example features the 3.4L direct-injection (DFI) flat-six, delivering linear power delivery through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is enhanced with factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and turn-in precision. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the vehicle shows no signs of bore scoring or rear main seal weeping. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free, while the undercarriage retains its factory-fresh cosmoline coating. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero track hours, offering a pure analog driving experience in a technologically optimized package.",
      "price": 48500.0,
